snippet.title: The 7th Circle - Trailer
snippet.description:
"The 7th Circle", a horror based Dungeon Crawler RPG, is now available for Windows and Linux on Steam. If you like classic crpg from the 90s, check this game.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/832710/The_7th_Circle/
http://www.68kstudios.com
